show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/gBn6Hh
show.description: Nurse Ananya Sharma’s life takes a shocking turn when a deal to save her brother’s life binds her to ruthless mafia kingpin Robin Shetty in a one-year contract marriage. As betrayals, rival gangs, and deadly secrets close in, Ananya must navigate love, fear, and the dangerous world of a man who will kill to protect her. Watch Now!
